%N A048901 Indices of hexagonal numbers which are also heptagonal.
%C A048901 As n increases, this sequence is approximately geometric with common ratio r = lim_{n->oo} a(n)/a(n-1) = (2 + sqrt(5))^4 = 161 + 72*sqrt(5). - _Ant King_, Dec 24 2011
%D A048901 Elena Deza and Michel Marie Deza, Figurate numbers, World Scientific Publishing (2012), page 39.
%H A048901 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A048901/b048901.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..200</a>
